%20a%20selfie.%20Right%3A%20A%20view%20out%20of%20a%20airplane%20window%20with%20a%20wing%20in%20view.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65579ccf22cf74a573995f0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMalick%20Mercier%2C%20left%2C%20commutes%20across%20the%20country%20for%20work.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Malick%20Mercier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFlight%20attendant%20Malick%20Mercier%20lives%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20but%20works%20out%20of%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he%20gets%20assigned%20to%20more%20interesting%20trips%20from%20New%20York%20City%20and%20the%20planes%20are%20nicer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20hardest%20parts%20of%20supercommuting%20is%20making%20sure%20he%20gets%20to%20work%20on%20time%2C%20Mercier%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Malick%20Mercier%2C%2024%2C%20about%20his%20commute%20to%20and%20from%20work%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%20for%20a%20major%20airline%20based%20in%20the%20northeast.%20He%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40highvibey%2Fvideo%2F7270606187341548843%3F_r%3D1%26_t%3D8hFizSnAiGF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Echronicles%20the%20commute%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20loved%20aviation.%20Growing%20up%20I%20was%20just%20super%20obsessed%20with%20planes.%20I%20had%20always%20dreamt%20of%20being%20a%20flight%20attendant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20when%20I%20was%20starting%2C%20and%20I'm%20glad%20I%20did.%20I%20was%20living%20with%20my%20mom%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20paying%20rent%20at%20all.%20But%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20the%20West.%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20somewhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20a%20flight%20attendant%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20only%20moment%20of%20your%20life%20when%20you%20can%20live%20somewhere%20else%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20crazy%20to%20think%20you%20could%20live%20wherever%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20in%20January%20of%20this%20year.%20My%20airline%20doesn't%20even%20have%20a%20base%20in%20Utah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223006%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20taking%20a%20selfie%20in%20a%20flight%20attendant%20uniform.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65579d144ca513d8242b793a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222415%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMercier%20poses%20for%20a%20selfie%20in%20uniform.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Malick%20Mercier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20really%20know%20anyone%20in%20Utah%20and%20it%20was%20cold.%20It%20was%20literally%20bringing%20my%20energy%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20there'd%20be%20more%20creative%20people%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20I%20was%20finding%20myself%20really%20happy%20here%20on%20layovers.%20I%20started%20thinking%20maybe%20this%20should%20be%20where%20I%20should%20be%2C%20and%20then%20it%20really%20worked%20out%20seamlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20commute%20to%20work%20can%20be%20up%20to%20eight%20hours%20depending%20on%20the%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20doesn't%20know%20where%20you%20are%2C%20they%20just%20expect%20you%20to%20show%20up.%20I%20make%20the%20commute%20about%20four%20times%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sometimes%20take%20three%20buses%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20time%20of%20day%2C%20to%20get%20to%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20International%20Airport%20employee%20bus%2C%20and%20then%20that%20will%20be%20my%20fourth%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20book%20the%20flight%20the%20night%20before%20if%20it's%20my%20airline.%20If%20it's%20another%20airline%2C%20we%20can't%20book%20it.%20We%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gate%20and%20ask%20them%20to%20be%20on%20the%20flight.%20So%20sometimes%20I'm%20really%20risking%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20check-in%20area%20of%20an%20airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65577aab4ca513d8242b4665%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221105%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMercier%20books%20his%20commuting%20flight%20only%20a%20day%20in%20advance%20with%20his%20airline.%20If%20he%20wants%20to%20fly%20on%20a%20different%20airline%2C%20he%20asks%20for%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20gate.%3Cp%3Estellalevi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20days%20when%20it's%20almost%20six%20hours%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20even%20counting%20the%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20or%20two%20hours%20it%20takes%20me%20to%20get%20to%20LAX%20if%20I%20don't%20Uber.%20Then%20you're%20looking%20at%20a%20five-%20to%20eight-hour%20commute.%20I%20feel%20like%20seven%20is%20the%20average%20commute%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20my%20favorite%20thing%20to%20do%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20plane.%20Although%20you're%20not%20being%20paid%2C%20it's%20a%20ton%20of%20time%20where%20you%20could%20totally%20be%20growing%20in%20something%20else.%20You%20could%20be%20reading%20a%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20get%20to%20the%20airport%20I'm%20working%20out%20of%2C%20I'll%20change%20into%20my%20uniform.%20I'll%20work%20three%20flights%20in%20one%20day%20after%20commuting%20and%20then%20get%20the%20layover.%20I%20can't%20do%20four%2C%20four%20is%20when%20I%20start%20crying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20poses%20with%20flamingos.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65579e2836d588dc55d26c4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMercier%20on%20a%20recent%20layover%20in%20Aruba.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Malick%20Mercier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20New%20York%20is%20a%20bigger%20base%2C%20New%20York%20crew%20members%20at%20my%20airline%20get%20a%20whole%20package%20based%20on%20our%20base%20and%20all%20the%20places%20we%20can%20go.%20I%20just%20got%20back%20from%20Guatemala.%20If%20I%20was%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20I%20would%20never%20have%20been%20offered%20that%20layover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20up%20until%20recently%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20crew%20members%20were%20basically%20exclusively%20working%20on%20one%20plane%20for%20the%20most%20part.%20People%20don't%20really%20think%20of%20that%2C%20but%20it's%20kind%20of%20like%20your%20office%20when%20you're%20up%20there%20for%20hours%20and%20hours.%20So%20you%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20nice%20one%20or%20the%20planes%20you%20like%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20really%20love%20my%20job%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20put%20up%20with%20the%20long%20commute%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECommuting%20is%20really%20hard%20depending%20on%20the%20day%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20you%20are%20trusted%20as%20a%20professional%20who's%20going%20to%20show%20up%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20have%20commuting%20troubles%2C%20we%20call%20it%20out%20of%20position.%20Thankfully%20I've%20never%20had%20to%20call%2C%20but%20it%20is%20really%20tough%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20a%20commute%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20was%20commuting%20home%2C%20thankfully%20%E2%80%94%20from%20JFK%20to%20LA.%20This%20is%20when%20I%20lived%20in%20Utah.%20We%20diverted%20to%20Long%20Beach%20after%20two%20go-arounds%20because%20the%20wind%20and%20the%20weather%20was%20so%20bad%20in%20LA%2C%20and%20then%20we%20flew%20from%20Long%20Beach%20to%20LA.%20The%20power%20went%20out%20in%20the%20terminal%20and%20I%20needed%20to%20still%20connect%20the%20flight%20to%20Salt%20Lake.%20I%20don't%20even%20remember%20how%20many%20hours%20it%20was%2C%20but%20it%20took%20forever.%20So%20those%20are%20the%20commuting%20moments%20that%20are%20really%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20smiles%20next%20to%20Hoda%20Kotb.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65579d8c36d588dc55d26bb7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221869%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMercier%20snapped%20a%20selfie%20with%20%26quot%3BToday%26quot%3B%20coanchor%20Hoda%20Kotb%20after%20running%20into%20her%20at%20JFK.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Malick%20Mercier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20flight%20attendants%20say%20commuting%20is%20basically%20a%20second%20job%2C%20and%20it%20does%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20You%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20flight%20schedules%20ahead%20of%20time%20and%20book%20ahead%20of%20time.%20I%20definitely%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20going%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20super%20cool%20that%20it's%20a%20flexible%20job%20because%20I'm%20able%20to%20travel%20for%20work%2C%20and%20then%20I%20learn%20so%20much%20about%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I'd%20keep%20commuting%20as%20long%20as%20I%20was%20this%20passionate%20about%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20that's%20what%20it%20comes%20down%20to.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20there's%20any%20job%20like%20this%20where%20you're%20exploring%20new%20cities%20or%20learning%20about%20things%20in%20real%20life%20and%20getting%20to%20meet%20so%20many%20different%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlenty%20of%20people%20are%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20it%20worth%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20I%20feel%20like%2C%20yes%2C%20because%20this%20is%20my%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20was%20a%20different%20job%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20that%20I%20would%20commute%20this%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommuter-la-to-nyc-flight-attendant-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700478242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65579ccf22cf74a573995f0a%3Ff