3E%3Cp%3ELoeb%20provided%20several%20rebuttals%20to%20the%20analysis.%20He%20cited%20team%20member%2C%20Dr%20Jim%20Lem%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Mining%20Engineering%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Technology%20in%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20region%20where%20the%20expedition%20was%20carried%2C%20should%20have%20no%20coal%20mineralization.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20spherules%20have%20more%20iron%20than%20coal%20ash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhere%20did%20the%20mysterious%20metal%20spherules%20come%20from%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELoeb's%20decision%20to%20seek%20out%20these%20spherules%20came%20from%20a%20high-stakes%20gamble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F24%2Fmagazine%2Favi-loeb-alien-hunter.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20scientist's%20team%20had%20uncovered%20partially%20classified%20governmental%20records%20suggesting%20an%20object%20had%20exploded%20near%20Earth%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20analysis%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20letter%20from%20US%20Space%20Command%2C%20suggested%20the%20fireball%20could%20have%20come%20from%20an%20object%20that%20had%20traveled%20from%20interstellar%20space%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20left%20Loeb%20wondering%20if%20the%202014%20object%20was%20an%20extraterrestrial%20probe%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20his%20theory%2C%20Loeb%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20recover%20debris%20from%20the%20object%2C%20which%20would%20have%20landed%20near%20Papua%20New%20Guinea.%20He%20commandeered%20a%20magnetic%20%26quot%3Brake%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20dredge%20under%20thousands%20of%20feet%20of%20water%2C%20an%20expedition%20that%20received%20%241.5%20million%20backing%20from%20a%20cryptocurrency%20magnate%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn't%20Loeb's%20first%20foray%20into%20the%20murky%20world%20of%20alien%20hunting.%20He%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20Oumuamua%2C%20a%20rare%20interstellar%20rocky%20object%20shaped%20like%20a%20cigar%20that%20flew%20a%20bizarre%20pattern%20as%20it%20passed%20Earth%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falien-object-close-to-earth-in-2017-says-harvard-professor-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20likely%20a%20piece%20of%20alien%20tech.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20claim%20has%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterstellar-object-oumuamua-part-of-planet-not-aliens-study-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20been%3C%2Fa%3E%20heavily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fcontent%2Farticle%2Fmystery-our-first-interstellar-visitor-may-be-solved%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisputed.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%20expedition%20could%20have%20failed%20if%20the%20spherules%20weren't%20magnetic%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%20But%20the%20team%20recovered%20hundreds%20of%20metallic%20spherules%2C%20tiny%20spheres%20that%20are%20the%20hallmark%20of%20debris%20left%20behind%20by%20meteorites%20when%20molten%20rock%20burns%20through%20the%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20of%20the%2057%20spherules%20he%20analyzed%20from%20the%20bunch%20were%20indeed%20bizarre%2C%20Loeb%20and%20co-authors%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2308.15623%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%20published%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20vetted%20by%20peer%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20made%20of%20an%20excess%20of%20beryllium%2C%20lanthanum%2C%20and%20uranium%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bnever%20seen%20before%26quot%3B%20composition%20for%20the%20tiny%20spheres%2C%20per%20the%20study.%20The%20spheres%20also%20carried%20bizarre%20iron%20isotopes%2C%20versions%20of%20atoms%2C%20which%20altogether%20were%20%26quot%3Bsupporting%20its%20interstellar%20origin%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20study%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDubbing%20these%20five%20spherules%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2308.15623%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeLaU%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Loeb%20and%20his%20colleagues%20went%20an%20extra%20step%20in%20their%20interpretation.%20They%20stated%20in%20their%20paper%20these%20%26quot%3Bmay%20reflect%20an%20extraterrestrial%20technological%20origin%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20they%20noted%20the%20claim%20required%20further%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fragments%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20a%20spacecraft%20from%20another%20civilization%20or%20some%20technological%20gadget%2C%26quot%3B%20Loeb%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Favi-loeb-harvard-professor-alien-technology-fragments-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20controversial%20take%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20scientists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-alien-hunters-debunk-alien-tech-discovery-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equickly%20distanced%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Loeb%20and%20colleagues'%20interpretation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20agreed%20that%20the%20bizarre%20composition%20of%20the%20BeLaU%20spherules%20could%20suggest%20an%20extra-terrestrial%20origin%20but%20questioned%20the%20claim%20they%20were%20necessarily%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhave-we-really-found-the-first-samples-from-beyond-the-solar-system-the-evidence-is-not-convincing-212789%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutside%20of%20the%20solar%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Others%20analyzing%20the%202014%20object%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2311.07699.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisagreed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20have%20come%20from%20interstellar%20space%2C%20and%20suggested%20the%20spherule%20composition%20could%20have%20come%20from%20the%20solar%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoeb%20disagreed%20with%20those%20he%20called%20his%20%26quot%3Blazy%20critics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20answer%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Loeb%20said%20that%20coal%20ash%20would%20not%20have%20been%20magnetic%20enough%20to%20be%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20dredging%20equipment%20they%20used%20to%20collect%20them%2C%20which%20used%20magnets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Loeb%2C%20his%20team's%20own%20analysis%20comparing%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20spherules%20and%20coal%20ash%2C%20conducted%20by%20his%20collaborators%20Stein%20Jacobsen%20at%20Harvard%20University%20and%20Roald%20Tagle%20from%20the%20Bruker%20Corporation%20in%20Germany%2C%20%26quot%3Bfound%20the%20two%20to%20be%20completely%20different%20in%20many%20elements%20including%20iron%2C%20silicon%20or%20aluminum.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20way%20that%20the%20two%20can%20be%20confused%20for%20one%20another.%20We%20are%20bewildered%20that%20the%20association%20of%20our%20spherules%20with%20coal%20ash%20was%20even%20suggested%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20his%20research%20teams%20are%20currently%20analyzing%20the%20remaining%2093%25%20of%20the%20nearly%20800%20spherules%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20surprising%20that%20anyone%20would%20state%20decisively%20that%20the%20spherules%20are%20coal%20ash%20without%20having%20access%20to%20the%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20to%20determine%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20spherules%20is%20through%20a%20careful%20scientific%20analysis%20which%20we%20are%20currently%20conducting%20with%20the%20best%20instruments%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20full%20analysis%20of%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20spherules%20will%20be%20reported%20once%20it%20is%20finished%2C%20Loeb%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGallardo%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20by%20BI%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetal-ball-ocean-harvard-professor-alien-industrial-waste-loeb-spherule-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700477473000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65574ffa22cf74a573991c8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetal-ball-ocean-harvard-professor-alien-industrial-waste-loeb-spherule-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Controversial%20Harvard%20Professor%20Avi%20Loeb%20ruffled%20feathers%20after%20claiming%20metal%20spherules%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20were%20alien%20tech.%20Now%2C%20there's%20another%20theory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mguenot%40businessinsider.com%20(Marianne%20Guenot)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetal-ball-ocean-harvard-professor-alien-industrial-waste-loeb-spherule-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20die%20as%20indoor%20stadium%20collapses%20in%20Telangana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700477431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105357183%2Cimgsize-916989.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2F2-killed-as-under-construction-indoor-stadium-collapses-in-telanganas-rangareddy-district-10-injured%2Farticleshow%2F105357194.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajendernagar%20DCP%2C%20Jagdeeshwar%20Reddy%2C%20said%20that%20one%20body%20has%20been%20recovered%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20retrieve%20another%20victim%20from%20the%20debris.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2F2-killed-as-under-construction-ind