ticise%20the%20government%20%E2%80%93%20are%20facing%20police%20cases%20or%20are%20already%20in%20jail.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20incidents%20of%20the%20detention%20of%20journalists%20associated%20with%20the%20news%20portal%20NewsClick%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-new-york-times-solidarity-statement%5C%22%3Ethe%20arrest%20of%20its%20founder%20and%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20the%20human%20resource%20chief%20Amit%20Chakravarty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20reappearance%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-is-the-indian-state-reigniting-a-13-year-old-case-against-arundhati-roy%5C%22%3Ecriminal%20case%20filed%20way%20back%20in%202010%20against%20Arundhati%20Roy%2C%20author%2C%20and%20Sheikh%20Showkat%20Hussain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Kashmir%20University%20professor%2C%20are%20clear%20examples%20of%20the%20onslaught%20on%20democratic%20values.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20almost%20seems%20as%20if%20democratic%20rights%20are%20the%20price%20one%20has%20to%20pay%20to%20enter%20into%20or%20live%20in%20this%20Amrit%20Kaal.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20how%20useful%20is%20the%20term%20totalitarianism%20to%20understand%20the%20predicament%20India%20is%20facing%20today%3F%20To%20pose%20the%20question%20differently%2C%20has%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20managed%20to%20totalise%20every%20domain%20and%20every%20strata%20of%20life%20in%20India%20to%20accept%20it%20as%20an%20invincible%20force%3F%20This%20might%20be%20their%20ultimate%20goal%20but%20to%20assume%20we%20are%20already%20there%20is%20a%20bit%20premature%20and%20can%20only%20cause%20hopelessness%20and%20despair.%20It%20would%20also%20be%20wrong%20to%20assume%20that%20there%20are%20no%20totalitarian%20tendencies%20in%20India%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fit-turns-out-modis-amrit-kaal-is-also-a-ruthless-kaal%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520semi%252Ddemocratic%252C%2520quasi%252D%2Ckroor%2520kaal%2520or%2520Ruthless%2520Era.%5C%22%3EIt%20Turns%20Out%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20is%20Also%20a%20Ruthless%20Kaal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20aspirations%20of%20any%20totalitarian%20regime%20is%20to%20make%20the%20populace%20subservient%20to%20its%20world%20views.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20it%20finds%20its%20direct%20opponents%20in%20the%20media%2C%20the%20fourth%20pillar%20of%20liberal%20democracy%2C%20and%20the%20proponents%20of%20human%20rights%20values.%20In%20this%20domain%20the%20Modi%20government%20seems%20to%20have%20succeeded%20a%20great%20deal%20by%20slapping%20cases%20often%20invoking%20the%20stringent%20UAPA%2C%20leaving%20journalists%20and%20human%20rights%20activists%20to%20turn%20only%20to%20the%20judicial%20system.%20Here%2C%20most%20of%20the%20legal%20remedy%20attained%2C%20even%20though%20limited%2C%20has%20come%20from%20the%20supreme%20judicial%20authority%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Supreme%20court%20of%20India%20located%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20This%20also%20shows%20the%20extreme%20difficulty%20in%20gaining%20this%20remedial%20measure%20available%20for%20democratic%20existence%20in%20contemporary%20India.%20With%20the%20limited%20resources%20%E2%80%93%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20smart%20lawyers%20who%20are%20ready%20to%20take%20up%20these%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20it%20may%20not%20be%20long%20before%20this%20remedial%20measure%20experiences%20absolute%20exhaustion%2C%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20the%20success%20of%20totalitarian%20aspiration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20main%20actors%20in%20this%20story%20%E2%80%93%20the%20dissenting%20voices%20who%20are%20targeted%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%93%20are%20also%20those%20who%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20their%20democratic%20rights%20while%20exercising%20them.%20They%20are%20an%20educated%20lot%2C%20often%20urban%20and%20with%20reasonable%20access%20to%20judicial%20remedial%20measures.%20They%20are%20cornered%20today%20not%20only%20by%20the%20powerful%20government%20machinery%20but%20also%20by%20a%20large%20army%20of%20those%20who%20control%20the%20terms%20of%20public%20debate%20in%20the%20mainstream%20and%20social%20media.%20They%20brand%20them%20%E2%80%98urban%20Naxals%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98anti-nationals%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20abusive%20terms.%20They%20are%20seen%20as%20an%20impediment%20which%20is%20stalling%20the%20establishment%20of%20Amrit%20Kaal%20in%20India%20and%20its%20conversion%20into%20Bharat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20does%20not%20mean%20the%20end%20of%20hope%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDemocratic%20existence%20in%20a%20country%20like%20India%20cannot%20only%20be%20imagined%20purely%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20ideals%20of%20liberty%2C%20free%20speech%2C%20fraternity%20or%20secularism.%20The%20large%20majority%20of%20the%20populace%20do%20not%20carry%20out%20their%20everyday%20life%20by%20being%20conscious%20of%20their%20democratic%20rights%20as%20citizens.%20Citizenship%20for%20them%20may%20only%20mean%20availing%20themselves%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20governmental%20initiatives%20like%20health%20care%20or%20public%20distribution%20system%20or%20the%20right%20to%20vote%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjournalism-in-modis-amrit-kaal-is-risky-business%5C%22%3EJournalism%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20Is%20Risky%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECitizenship%20is%20one%20of%20the%20modes%20of%20existence%20in%20India%20for%20them.%20But%20it%20is%20an%20important%20mode.%20It%20may%20be%20because%20of%20this%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20people%20came%20out%20to%20protest%20when%20they%20felt%20a%20threat%20to%20this%20mode%20of%20existence%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Indian%20parliament%20passing%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20in%202019.%20It%20was%20a%20fight%20for%20the%20right%20to%20exist%20and%20not%20for%20upholding%20the%20ideals%20of%20liberal%20democracy.%20It%20is%20also%20possible%20to%20see%20another%20major%20protest%20against%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%93%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20protest%20against%20the%20now-scrapped%20central%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20also%20as%20a%20fight%20of%20this%20sort.%20It%20may%20look%20simplistic%20but%20most%20powerful%20and%20enduring%20fights%20are%20often%20fights%20which%20are%20necessitated%20when%20our%20existence%20as%20bare%20beings%20are%20threatened.%20These%20may%20be%20some%20of%20the%20most%20visible%20examples%20of%20struggles%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20for%20democratic%20life%20of%20this%20sort%2C%20but%20there%20may%20have%20been%20many%20more%20unnoticed%20ones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20here%20that%20totalitarianism%20would%20find%20its%20limits%2C%20and%20fail%20to%20establish%20itself.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20if%20people%20fall%20prey%20to%20religious%20majoritarianism%2C%20and%20get%20swayed%20by%20the%20charisma%20of%20an%20all%20powerful%20image%20of%20the%20leader%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20questions%20of%20subsistence%20and%20sheer%20existence%2C%20getting%20co-opted%20may%20not%20be%20a%20possibility.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20large%20majority%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20populace%20finds%20its%20existence%20in%20between%20political%20extremes.%20It%20will%20be%20from%20these%20quarters%20that%20unexpected%20voices%20are%20likely%20to%20emerge%20and%20save%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EAshokan%20Nambiar%20teaches%20at%20Manipal%20Centre%20for%20Humanities%2C%20MAHE%2C%20Manipal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2