2C%20India%20lost.%20That%20just%20about%20sums%20up%20the%20World%20Club%20finals%20result%20on%20Sunday%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20the%20newspapers%20play%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Champions%20Nonetheless%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20headline%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98Crown%20on%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20Head%2C%20Heartbreak%20for%20our%20Heroes%E2%80%99%20said%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20front%20page%20report%20talked%20about%20%E2%80%98An%20Indian%20team%20that%20had%20an%20imperious%20run%20up%20throughout%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20demolishing%20all%20opposition%20with%20a%20gladiatorial%20swagger%2C%20finally%20had%20a%20bad%20day.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20did%20have%20a%20superb%20run%20up%20to%20the%20finals%2C%20not%20losing%20even%20a%20single%20match%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20have%20a%20%E2%80%98bad%20day%E2%80%99%20on%20Sunday.%20It%20was%20outplayed%20in%20every%20department%2C%20not%20the%20least%20in%20the%20fielding%20department%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Australians%20must%20have%20saved%20many%20runs%20simply%20by%20their%20outstanding%20fielding%2C%20the%20highlight%20of%20that%20being%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fwatch-travis-heads-stunning-catch-to-dismiss-rohit-sharma-in-world-cup-final%2Farticleshow%2F105331152.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuperb%20diving%20catch%20by%20Travis%20Head%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20dismiss%20a%20menacing%20looking%20Rohit%20Sharma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Australians%20played%20to%20a%20plan%2C%20even%20going%20in%20to%20field%20first%2C%20which%20seemed%20strange%2C%20given%20that%20this%20was%20an%20occasion%20to%20build%20a%20good%20score%20and%20bowl%20the%20second%20team%20out.%20But%20then%20they%20held%20Indians%20on%20a%20tight%20leash%2C%20not%20allowing%20them%20to%20hit%20more%20than%204%20fours%20in%20the%20last%2040%20overs%20after%20the%20abandon%20with%20which%20boundaries%20were%20knocked%20about%20in%20the%20first%2010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20this%20was%20on%20a%20pitch%20which%20the%20Indian%20establishment%20%E2%80%93%20the%20all%20powerful%20BCCI%20%E2%80%93%20had%20specially%20prepared%20to%20allegedly%20help%20the%20Indians%2C%20which%20the%20Australian%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theage.com.au%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Ffever-pitch-australia-to-wait-on-wicket-before-selecting-cup-final-team-20231118-p5ekzd.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20captain%2C%20too%2C%20reportedly%20raised%20concerns%20about%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20If%20the%20home%20team%20too%20was%20dissatisfied%2C%20it%20will%20never%20be%20known%20because%20no%20Indian%20player%20will%20ever%20speak%20about%20it%20publicly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EA%20similar%20controversy%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsport%2F2023%2Fnov%2F15%2Findia-accused-over-pitch-switch-for-new-zealand-cricket-world-cup-semi-final%5C%22%3Eerupted%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20India-New%20Zealand%20semi%20final%20match%20at%20Wankhede%20stadium%20that%20the%20pitch%20had%20been%20switched%20at%20the%20last%20moment%20because%20it%20would%20help%20the%20Indian%20team.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENonetheless%2C%20the%20teams%20got%20on%20with%20it%2C%20and%20the%20better%20team%20won.%20And%2C%20it%20was%20a%20hopelessly%20one-sided%20match%2C%20which%20point%20seems%20to%20have%20escaped%20much%20of%20the%20reporting%20on%20it.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20tight%20game%20%E2%80%93%20240%20all%20out%20in%2050%20overs%20versus%20241%20for%204%20in%2043%20overs%20cannot%20be%20called%20that.%20It%20was%20a%20walkover%2C%20in%20which%20one%20side%20simply%20could%20not%20muster%20up%20the%20skills%20or%20the%20imagination%20to%20put%20up%20a%20fair%20fight.%20This%20did%20not%20look%20like%20a%20machine%20in%20which%20every%20component%20was%20firing%20and%20which%20had%20raised%20the%20hopes%20and%20confidence%20of%20every%20Indian%20cricket%20fan.%20This%20looked%20a%20demoralised%2C%20stuttering%20engine%20where%20no%20one%20%E2%80%93%20barring%20Sharma%20and%20the%20ever%20reliable%20Virat%20Kohli%20%E2%80%93%20performed%20to%20their%20true%20potential.%20The%20others%2C%20batters%20and%20bowlers%2C%20simply%20collapsed.%20The%20Australians%2C%20who%20began%20the%20tournament%20with%20two%20big%20losses%2C%20against%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20won%20nine%20games%20after%20that%2C%20including%20the%20superb%20fight%20back%20against%20minnows%20Afghanistan%2C%20when%20they%20won%20after%20being%20down%2091-7%2C%20had%20begun%20to%20peak%20towards%20the%20final.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20more%20than%20just%20the%20performance%20on%20the%20field%20with%20the%20bat%20and%20the%20ball%2C%20the%20Indian%20team%20had%20to%20contend%20with%20enormous%20subliminal%20pressure%20that%20went%20beyond%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20game.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20has%20been%20said%20about%20home%20team%20advantage%20%E2%80%93%20over%20100%2C000%20fans%20fully%20backing%20the%20Indians%20can%20be%20a%20morale%20booster.%20But%20it%20can%20be%20a%20burden%20too.%20And%20in%20Ahmedabad%20it%20definitely%20was%20an%20albatross%20around%20the%20Indians%E2%80%99%20neck.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENever%20has%20there%20been%20a%20more%20graceless%20and%20partisan%20crowd%20than%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20which%20roared%20every%20time%20an%20Indian%20player%20hit%20a%20four%20and%20did%20not%20even%20cursorily%20applaud%20when%20the%20Australians%20took%20a%20wicket.%20Ahmedabad%2C%20never%20among%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20or%20even%20India%E2%80%99s%20great%20stadia%2C%20has%20become%20prominent%20only%20to%20satisfy%20one%20man%E2%80%99s%20ego.%20Gujarat%20is%20his%20domain%20where%20he%20can%20do%20no%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20he%20got%20a%20stadium%20refurbished%2C%20had%20it%20named%20after%20himself%20and%20opened%20it%20for%20the%20masses%20in%20his%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGujarat%20has%20no%20cricket%20culture%20like%20Mumbai%20or%20sporting%20crowds%20like%20in%20Chennai.%20These%20things%20cannot%20be%20developed%20overnight.%20But%20it%20was%20decreed%20that%20Ahmedabad%20must%20get%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20stadium%20and%20it%20was%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20same%20venue%20where%20Pakistani%20player%20Mohammed%20Rizwan%20was%20heckled%20and%20the%20crowds%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahmedabadmirror.com%2Fcontroversy-erupts-over-jai-shri-ram-chants-directed-at-pakistan-cricketer-in-india-pakistan-world-cup-match%2F81865637.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ekept%20up%20a%20chant%20of%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20crowds%20cheered%20the%20Pakistani%20team%20when%20it%20arrived%20in%20Hyderabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20organisers%20goofed%20on%20the%20trophy%20presentation%20to%20the%20Australian%20captain%20and%20many%20Indian%20players%20left%20before%20it%2C%20perhaps%20not%20wanting%20to%20see%20Pat%20Cummins%20lift%20it.%20In%20the%20Australian%20media%20and%20on%20X%2C%20they%20had%20a%20good%20laugh%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20Ahmedabad%20was%20chosen%20for%20the%20final%20and%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20took%20time%20off%20from%20his%20busy%20schedule%20to%20attend%2C%20no%20doubt%20convinced%20that%20the%20Indians%20would%20win%20and%20he%20would%20be%20on%20the%20ground%20handing%20over%20the%20cup.%20His%20home%20minister%2C%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20whose%20son%20just%20happens%20to%20be%20running%20the%20super%20rich%20BCCI%2C%20was%20with%20him.%20Scattered%20in%20the%20VIP%20seats%2C%20were%20sundry%20Bollywood%20superstars%20such%20as%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Deepika%20Padukone%2C%20former%20cricketers%20like%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20sitting%20with%20the%20Sadhguru%20and%20such%20like.%20Kapil%20Dev%2C%20who%20captained%20the%20team%20in%201983%20when%20India%20won%20the%20first%20World%20Cup%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Ficc-world-cup-i-wasnt-invited-for-the-final-kapil-dev%2Farticle67552064.ece%5C%22%3Ewas%20not%20invited%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20through%20the%20tournament%2C%20the%20media%2C%20especially%20the%20electronic%20one%2C%20have%20further%20built%20up%20the%20Indian%20team%20as%20invincible.%20The%20other%20teams%20might%20as%20well%20be%20non-existent.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20the%20media%20was%20full%20of%20realistic%20commentary%20and%20debate%20about%20the%20form%20of%20each%20team%20%E2%80%93%20this%20time%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiaforum.in%2Fsociety%2Fcricket-world-cup-india-india-and-about-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20was%20only%20about%20the%20Indian%20team%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20entire%20effort%20is%20to%20build%20up%20the%20narrative%20of%20India%20%C3%BCber%20alles%2C%20as%20India%2C%20which%20is%20now%20Bharat%20(tricolours%20in%20the%20stadium%20called%20it%20just%20that)%2C%20is%20the%20greatest%20in%20every%20field%20%E2%80%93%20in%20science%2C%20culture%2C%20medicine%2C%20economy%2C%20and%20wisdom.%20Barring%20a%20break%20of%20%E2%80%98a%20thousand%20years%20of%20slavery%E2%80%99%20that%20ended%20in%202014%2C%20India%20was%20always%20the%20font%20of%20all%20knowledge%20and%20now%20things%20are%20back%20on%20track.%20The%20media%20amplifies%20this%20message%20and%20the%20devotees%20lap%20it%20up.%20It%20all%20feeds%20right%20into%20the%20hyper-nationalism%20that%20has%20been%20built%20up%20by%20the%20current%20political%20dispensation.%20Everyone%20is%20happy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20public%20because%20it%20gives%20them%20something%20to%20hold%20on%20to%2C%20the%20politicians%20because%20it%20is%20to%20their%20advantage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVictory%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Sunday%20would%20have%20pumped%20it%20up%20further.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20the%20message%20would%20have%20gone%20out%20%E2%80%93%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20India%20had%20ever%20won%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20and%20it%20was%20only%20because%20of%20one%20man%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20vision%20and%20leadership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20almost%20feel%20sorry%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20It%20is%20full%20of%20enormously%20talented%20players%2C%20and%20is%20top%20of%20the%20heap%20in%20all%20forms%20of%20the%20game.%20It%20had%20a%20great%20run%20up%20to%20the%20finals%20on%20Sunday.%20It%20did%20not%20win%2C%20because%20the%20other%20team%20performed%20better.%20But%20the%20pressure%20it%20must%20have%20been%20under%20can%20get%20down%20anyone%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20the%20weight%20of%20expectations%20of%20the%20fans%20which%20is%20normal%20in%20any%20big%20match%2C%20but%20also%20the%20feeling%20that%20by%20losing%2C%20it%20will%20be%20letting%20down%20the%20nation%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700470220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20130341%2FF_UC24iWIAAm2ms.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-team-winner%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20crowds%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20showed%20little%20grace%20in%20applauding%20Australia%20and%20other%20teams%20playing%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-team-winner%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Today%20in%20history%3A%20International%20Space%20Station%20turns%2025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700469895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105352664%2Cimgsize-60122.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftoday-in-history-international-space-station-turns-25%2Farticleshow%2F105352598.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105352598.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EToday%20marks%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%2C%20symbolizing%20international%20collaboration%20in%20space%20exploration.%20With%20contributions%20from%20multiple%20countries%2C%20the%20ISS%20has%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20advancing%20our%20understanding%20of%20space%20and%20microgravity%20through%20scientific%20research.%20It%20has%20also%20served%20as%20a%20testbed%20for%20studying%20the%20effects%20of%20long-duration%20space%20missions%20on%20the%20human%20body%2C%20providing%20valuable%20knowledge%20for%20future%20endeavors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftoday-in-history-international-space-station-turns-25%2Farticleshow%2F105352598.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftoday-in-history-international-space-station-turns-25%2Famp_articleshow%2F105352598.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftoday-in-history-international-space-station-turns-25%2Famp_articleshow%2F105352598.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20dominate%20'ICC%20Team%20of%20the%20World%20Cup'%20with%20six%20players%22%2C%22co