C%22%3ENovember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20present%20at%20the%20venue%20to%20watch%20the%20two%20cricketing%20giants%20square%20off.%20He%20even%20handed%20over%20the%20World%20Cup%20trophy%20to%20Australia%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20team's%20triumph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20much-fancied%20India%20team%20led%20by%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20went%20into%20Sunday's%20final%20in%20front%20of%20nearly%20100%2C000%20fans%20in%20Ahmedabad%20undefeated%20and%20favourites%20to%20capture%20the%20one-day%20crown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20were%20outplayed%20by%20Pat%20Cummins'%20Australia%2C%20going%20down%20to%20a%20six-wicket%20defeat%20and%20leaving%20players%2C%20fans%20and%20pundits%20with%20a%20familiar%20feeling%20of%20bitter%20disappointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20record%20makes%20for%20painful%20reading%20for%20its%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20fanatical%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20last%20global%20title%20came%20a%20decade%20ago%20with%20the%202013%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunday%20was%20also%20India's%20second%20loss%20to%20the%20Australians%20in%20a%20final%20in%20five%20months%2C%20after%20they%20went%20down%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20decider%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20won%20the%20one-day%20World%20Cup%20in%201983%20and%202011%2C%20but%20then%20faltered%20at%20the%20semi-final%20stage%20in%202015%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20AFP%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700469180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4gqv4g6o_pm-modi-and-jadeja_625x300_20_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fravindra-jadeja-reveals-pm-mod