0Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20exchanging%20a%20handshake%20and%20hug.%20The%20event%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20a%20new%20era%20as%20India%20missed%20out%20on%20a%20third%20World%20Cup%20title.%20The%20seasoned%20trio%20of%20Kohli%2C%20Sharma%2C%20and%20Shami%20will%20continue%20their%20careers%2C%20but%20it%20is%20now%20the%20younger%20generation's%20duty%20to%20carry%20the%20team%20forward%20and%20create%20a%20fresh%20legacy.%20Players%20like%20Gill%2C%20Iyer%2C%20Gaikwad%2C%20Jaiswal%2C%20and%20Pant%20are%20expected%20to%20play%20pivotal%20roles%20in%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fgenerational-shift-evident-as-india-reflect-on-world-cup-loss%2Farticleshow%2F105351378.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20As%20A%20Sports%20Fan%2C%20I%20Am%20Angry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20the%20Indian%20World%20Cup%20winning%20Team%20of%201983%20issued%20this%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20distressed%20and%20disturbed%20at%20the%20unseemly%20visuals%20of%20our%20champion%20wrestlers%20being%20manhandled.%20We%20are%20also%20most%20concerned%20that%20they%20are%20thinking%20of%20dumping%20their%20hard-earned%20medals%20into%20the%20river%20Ganga.%20Those%20medals%20have%20involved%20years%20of%20effort%2C%20sacrifice%2C%20determination%20and%20grit%20and%20are%20not%20only%20their%20own%20but%20the%20nation's%20pride%20and%20joy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2019%20November%202023%2C%20Kapil's%20Devils%2C%20as%20those%20champions%20were%20fondly%20called%2C%20did%20not%20receive%20even%20an%20invitation%20to%20watch%20the%20final%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20sports%20fan%2C%20I%20am%20angry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrace.%20Good%20manners.%20Gratitude.%20Too%20much%20to%20ask%20for%20from%20those%20peddling%20jingoism%20in%20the%20name%20of%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENostalgia%2C%20they%20say%2C%20is%20a%20good%20antidote%20for%20anger.%20So%20let%20me%20share%20with%20you%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20on%2025%20June%201983.%20Frame%20by%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%2022.%20My%20two%20brothers%20along%20with%20four%20of%20our%20buddies%20(we%20used%20to%20work%20for%20a%20magazine%20edited%20by%20Tiger%20Pataudi%20called%20Sportsworld)%20decided%20to%20watch%20the%20Prudential%20World%20Cup%20final%20together.%20So%20we%20all%20assembled%20at%20the%20O'Brien%20family%20home%20in%20Jamir%20Lane%20in%20Kolkata.%20My%20ma%20never%20ever%20asked%20how%20many%20were%20coming%20for%20dinner%20-%20there%20were%20always%20'extras'%2C%20cricket%20or%20no%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERed%20ball%2C%20white%20jerseys%2C%2060%20over%20innings.%20Brand%20new%20colour%20TVs.%20In%20the%20previous%20two%20World%20Cups%2C%20India%20had%20won%20only%20one%20match%20(against%20East%20Africa)%20and%20lost%20every%20other%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20out%20early.%20Srikkanth%20played%20some%20crunchers%2C%20including%20an%20iconic%20on-one-knee%20square-drive%20off%20Roberts.%20Amarnath%20hooked%20Marshall%20for%20a%20four.%20The%20swagger%20of%20Sandeep%20Patil.%20Last-wicket%20partnership%20of%2022%20between%20Syed%20Kirmani%20and%20Balwinder%20Sandhu.%20183.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20read%20that%20during%20the%20innings%20break%2C%20Kapil%20Dev%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTeam%2C%20if%20this%20is%20not%20a%20winning%20total%2C%20then%20it's%20definitely%20a%20fighting%20total.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20remember%20who%20it%20was%20we%2020%20something-year-olds%20hustled%20to%20get%20us%20a%20few%20beers%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20share.%20I%20do%20remember%20the%20brand%3A%20high%20glycerine%20content%20Kalyani%20Black%20Label.%20But%20dad%20was%20drinking%20Black%20Label%20of%20another%20kind%20-%20whiskey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20wicket.%20Sandhu%20took%20Gordon%20Greenidge's%20off-stump%20when%20the%20opener%20from%20the%20West%20Indies%20offered%20no%20stroke.%20Viv%20Richards%20strutted%20in%2C%20nonchalantly%20chewing%20gum.%20Smashed%20seven%20boundaries%2C%20including%20three%20in%20an%20over%20off%20Madan%20Lal.%20Meanwhile%20in%20Jamir%20Lane%2C%20the%20seating%20had%20to%20be%20rearranged.%20Two%20of%20us%20were%20asked%20to%20go%20stand%20in%20the%20narrow%20balcony%20next%20to%20the%20living%20room.%20A%20third%20was%20asked%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20floor.%20Just%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20field%20placement%20needed%20to%20take%20a%20Caribbean%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20stage%20an%20Indian%20win%20looked%20unlikely.%20Almost%20impossible.%20Little%20wonder%20that%20my%20dad%2C%20who%20was%20always%20miserly%20about%20sharing%20his%20scotch%2C%20made%20a%20grand%20announcement%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20win%20I%20will%20open%20a%20new%20bottle%26quot%3B.%20I%20made%20an%20announcement%20as%20well%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20India%20wins%2C%20I%20will%20streak%20on%20the%20main%20road!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20Dev%20was%20about%20to%20take%20Madan%20Lal%20off.%20Madan%20Lal%20asked%20the%20captain%20to%20give%20him%20an%20extra%20over.%20Viv%20Richards%20went%20for%20the%20pull.%20The%20Indian%20skipper%20covered%20a%20lot%20of%20ground%20from%20mid-wicket%20to%20take%20a%20magical%20catch.%20Cricket%20pundits%20say%20this%20was%20the%20catch%20that%20turned%20that%20match.%20Travis%20Head's%20catch%20to%20dismiss%20Rohit%20Sharma%20did%20the%20same%20in%20the%202023%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20Larry%20Gomes%20and%20Clive%20Loyd%20went%20in%20quick%20succession.%20A%20stand%20between%20wicket-keeper%20Jeff%20Dujon%20and%20Malcolm%20Marshall%20threatened%20to%20get%20the%20West%20Indies%20back%20in%20the%20game.%20Man%20of%20the%20Match%20Mohinder%20Amarnath%20snuffed%20it%20out.%20Finally.%20Michael%20Holding%20LBW%20Amarnath.%20From%2050%2F1%2C%20West%20Indies%20all%20out%20for%20140.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20Dev%20on%20the%20balcony%20at%20Lords.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDad%20kept%20his%20promise%20and%20raised%20a%20toast.%20I%20happily%20kept%20my%20word%20and%20became%20the%20first%20streaker%20(the%20undies%20were%20always%20on%20though!)%20of%20the%20neighbourhood%20in%20south%20Kolkata%20where%20we%20grew%20up.%20Those%20were%20different%20days.%20So%20we%20don't%20have%20selfies%20or%20potentially%20viral%20videos%20as%20evidence%20from%20that%20evening%20of%20June%20in%201983.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seven%20of%20us%20who%20watched%20that%20match%20as%20twenty-year-olds%2C%20are%20now%20around%20sixty.%20During%20the%20final%20played%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20each%20one%20of%20us%20were%20merrily%20making%20predictions%20and%20passing%20expert%20comments%20on%20our%20WhatsApp%20group.%20My%20brother%20Barry%20and%20I%20live%20in%20Kolkata.%20My%20brother%20Andy%20and%20David%20McMahon%20in%20Australia.%20Purvez%20Captain%20in%20the%20USA.%20Pradeep%20Paul%20in%20Singapore.%20Christopher%20Jones%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricket%20matches%20come%20and%20go%2C%20friendships%20last%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700468220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fc5dhuhqk_kapil-dev-ani_625x300_20_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-a-sports-fan-i-am-angry-4588583%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cricket%20matches%20come%20and%20go%2C%20friendships%20last%20forever.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A141%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-a-sports-fan-i-am-angry-4588583%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A