20after%20information%20about%20the%20UFO%20near%20the%20Imphal%20airport%20was%20received%2C%20a%20Rafale%20fighter%20aircraft%20from%20a%20nearby%20airbase%20was%20scrambled%20to%20go%20and%20search%20for%20the%20UFO%2C%26quot%3B%20defence%20sources%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aircraft%20equipped%20with%20advanced%20sensors%20carried%20out%20low-level%20flying%20over%20the%20suspected%20area%20to%20look%20for%20the%20UFO%20but%20it%20did%20not%20find%20anything%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20after%20the%20first%20aircraft%20returned%2C%20one%20more%20Rafale%20fighter%20was%20sent%20for%20the%20search%20but%20the%20UFO%20was%20not%20seen%20around%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agencies%20concerned%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20the%20details%20of%20the%20UFO%20as%20there%20are%20videos%20of%20the%20UFO%20over%20the%20Imphal%20airport%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20Imphal%20airport%20was%20cleared%20for%20flying%2C%20the%20Shillong-headquartered%20Eastern%20Command%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20stated%20that%20it%20had%20activated%20its%20Air%20Defence%20response%20mechanism%20without%20giving%20any%20specific%20details%20of%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEastern%20Command%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20'X'%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIAF%20activated%20its%20Air%20Defence%20response%20mechanism%20based%20on%20visual%20inputs%20from%20Imphal%20airport.%20The%20small%20object%20was%20not%20seen%20thereafter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rafale%20fighters%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20are%20deployed%20at%20the%20Hashimara%20air%20base%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20keep%20flying%20from%20different%20air%20bases%20in%20the%20eastern%20sector%20along%20the%20China%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rafale%20fighters%20recently%20also%20took%20part%20in%20the%20mega%20Air%20Force%20exercise%20Poorvi%20Akash%20al