0has%20devised%20a%20five-option%20action%20plan%20to%20rescue%20those%20trapped%20inside%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel.%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Secretary%20Anurag%20Jain%20stated%20that%20five%20separate%20agencies%20will%20work%20on%20these%20alternatives%2C%20which%20involve%20drilling%20from%20three%20sides%20to%20access%20the%20trapped%20workers.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20decision%20to%20work%20on%20all%20fronts%20to%20save%20the%20precious%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rescue%20ops%20entered%20Day%209%2C%20here's%20NDTV's%20Ground%20Report%20from%20the%20collapsed%20Silkyara%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20operation%2C%20which%20involved%20drilling%20from%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20came%20to%20a%20halt%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20fault%20with%20a%20large%20American%20auger%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20now%20shifted%20their%20focus%20to%20alternative%20approaches%2C%20including%20creating%20two%20new%20tunnels%20to%20reach%20the%20trapped%20workers.%20One%20tunnel%20will%20be%20drilled%20horizontally%20from%20the%20right%20and%20left%20sides%20of%20the%20main%20tunnel%2C%20while%20the%20other%20will%20be%20drilled%20vertically%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20for%20the%20excavation%20of%20a%20vertical%20shaft.%20This%20vertical%20shaft%20will%20serve%20as%20an%20alternative%20route%20for%20reaching%20the%20trapped%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20plan%20to%20airlift%20heavy%20machinery%20to%20the%20site%20was%20abandoned%20due%20to%20logistical%20challenges.%20Authorities%20have%20determined%20that%20airlifting%20the%20heavy%20equipment%20is%20not%20feasible%20due%20to%20their%20immensely%20heavy%20weights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20heavy%20machine%20is%20required%20to%20access%20the%20top%20of%20the%20t