er%20exercise%20I%20set%20myself%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%20was%20to%20pick%20a%20second%20Indian%20XI%20from%20players%20not%20in%20the%20first-choice%20team.%20You%E2%80%99d%20have%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Ravichandra%20Ashwin%20and%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Sanju%20Samson.%20Maybe%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20to%20skipper%20and%20Umran%20Malik%20to%20bowl%20smoke.%20Crikey%2C%20they%E2%80%99d%20beat%20most%20international%20teams%3B%20they%E2%80%99d%20certainly%20flog%20the%20next-best%20Australians.%20By%20their%20abundance%20of%20talent%2C%20and%20by%20the%20game%E2%80%99s%20enjoying%20such%20precedence%2C%20India%20will%20always%20trade%20an%20advantage%20in%20the%20multi-format%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20always%20XI%20versus%20XI.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20timeworn%20%E2%80%98war%20minus%20the%20shooting%E2%80%99%20metaphor%20falls%20short%2C%20because%20the%20sporting%20battlefield%20is%20arbitrarily%20even%2C%20the%20forces%20are%20by%20consent%20restricted%2C%20and%20efforts%20at%20interference%20stand%20out%20%E2%80%93%20they%20can%20even%20be%20seen%20as%20slightly%20shameful.%20Prepare%20for%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20to%20argue%20that%20in%20view%20of%20their%20overwhelming%20contribution%20to%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20financial%20health%2C%20India%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20field%20fifteen%20players%20to%20everyone%20else%E2%80%99s%20eleven%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20to%20the%20final.%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20first%20glimmer%20is%20at%20the%20toss%2C%20affording%20Pat%20Cummins%20the%20opportunity%20to%20bat%20under%20the%20lights.%20Three%20of%20the%20four%20cup%20games%2C%20and%20both%20IPL%20finals%2C%20have%20been%20won%20by%20the%20pursuers%2C%20so%20the%20gamble%20seems%20worthwhile%3B%20nor%20is%20it%20so%20mercilessly%20hot%20that%2050%20overs%20in%20the%20field%20will%20be%20a%20punishment.%20Then%2C%20a%20tiny%20portent.%20Mitchell%20Starc%E2%80%99s%20second%20ball%20floats%20wide%20in%20search%20of%20shape%20back.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20thrashes%20and%20eyes%20swivel%20to%20the%20point%20boundary.%20But%20Travis%20Head%2C%20right%20where%20the%20data%20says%20he%20needs%20to%20be%2C%20tracks%20speedily%20left%20and%20saves%20two%20runs.%20And%20even%20as%20the%20Indians%20strain%20to%20get%20loose%2C%20they%20go%20on%20feeling%20an%20Australian%20check.%20At%20eight%20an%20over%2C%20they%20exceed%20their%20Cup%20power%20play%20average.%20But%20the%20Australian%20fielding%20probably%20saves%20a%20further%2020%20runs%2C%20and%20heralds%20the%20breakthrough%2C%20Head%20catching%20Rohit%2C%20running%20back%2C%20diving%20forward%2C%20celebrating%20perfunctorily.%20This%2C%20as%20Head%20described%20it%20later%2C%20was%20cricket%20in%20the%20best%20Australian%20vein.%20Thought%20he%20had%20no%20chance.%20Had%20a%20go%20anyway.%20Was%20surprised%20to%20catch%20it.%20Wasn%E2%80%99t%20inclined%20to%20make%20a%20fuss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20balls%20on%20from%20the%20Powerplay%2C%20India%20lose%20a%20third%2C%20and%20Australia%20are%20suddenly%20three%20further%20wickets%20from%20that%20invitingly%20elongated%20home%20tail%3A%20number%20eight%20Shami%2C%20whose%20highest%20score%20in%20100%20ODIs%20is%2025%3B%20number%20nine%20Bumrah%2C%20whose%20highest%20score%20in%2088%20ODIs%20is%2016.%20Sure%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20SKY%20to%20come%2C%20but%20he%E2%80%99s%20unproven%20in%20ODIs%2C%20and%20hardly%20a%20like-for-like%20swap%20with%20Hardik%20Pandya.%20So%2C%20now%20it%20is%20circumstances%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Australians%2C%20bearing%20down%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20fourth%20wicket%20partners.%20Cummins%20distributes%20the%20bowling%20load%20widely%3B%20the%20part-timers%20get%20off%20lightly%3B%20the%20fielding%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20overthrows%20aside%2C%20remains%20wonderfully%20vigilant.%20India%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20game%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20while%20since%20they%20have%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20cameras%20dwell%20on%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20handsome%20features%20as%20he%20achieves%20his%20fifth%20consecutive%20score%20of%2050%20or%20more%2C%20the%20game%20has%20commenced%20an%20arc%20away%20from%20the%20hosts.%20Whether%20Kohli%20and%20K.L.%20Rahul%20spent%20too%20long%20over%20their%20runs%20will%20long%20be%20debated%3B%20after%20all%2C%20people%20still%20wonder%20whether%20Mike%20Brearley%20and%20Geoffrey%20Boycott%20spent%20too%20long%20over%20theirs%20in%20the%201979%20final.%20I%E2%80%99m%20more%20inclined%20to%20be%20forgiving%3A%20the%20design%20flaw%20of%20the%20order%20was%20always%20bound%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20India%20at%20some%20stage%2C%20likeliest%20of%20all%20in%20the%20final%20against%20the%20strongest%20opposition.%20Kohli%2C%20generally%20so%20decisive%2C%20seldom%20if%20ever%20drags%20on%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dismissal%20characteristic%20of%20conglomerated%20thoughts.%20Now%20he%20does%2C%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20with%20so%20little%20recent%20batting%2C%20is%20all%20at%20sea%20against%20the%20reversing%20ball.%20It%20all%20gets%20very%20messy%20until%20last-man-picked%20Marnus%20Labuschagne%20ends%20it%20with%20his%20fourth%20run%20out%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it%E2%80%99s%20over%20to%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20other%20selection%20long%20shot%2C%20Head%2C%20included%20in%20the%20squad%20while%20still%20convalescent%2C%20and%20having%20gone%20six%20weeks%20without%20a%20hit%20before%20reappearing%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Dharamshala.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20dew%2C%20240%20is%20effectively%20210%3B%20thanks%20to%20Head%2C%20Australia%20take%2015%20off%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20first%20over.%20Australia%20are%20three%20down%20after%20seven%20overs%20but%20have%20already%20reduced%20the%20required%20run%20rate%20to%204.5.%20Shami%E2%80%99s%20lethality%20to%20left-handers%20does%20not%20prevent%20Head%20from%20picking%20two%20boundaries%20off%20him%20in%20the%20last%20over%20of%20the%20Powerplay%2C%20affording%20Labuschagne%20time%20to%20settle%20the%20way%20he%20likes%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20Head%20has%20a%2058-ball%20fifty%20by%20the%20time%20Labuschagne%20first%20finds%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20all%20this%2C%20so%20further%20detail%20is%20probably%20superfluous.%20So%20let%E2%80%99s%20just%20concentrate%20on%20that%20brooding%20atmosphere%2C%20that%20eddying%20disbelief.%20When%20cricket%20and%20crowd%20feed%20off%20one%20another%20in%20India%2C%20there%20can%20be%20a%20feeling%20of%20playing%20against%20a%20whole%20country.%20Quiet%2C%20such%20as%20that%20now%20pervading%20Modi%20Stadium%2C%20is%20oppositely%20telling.%20The%20crowd%20know%20it.%20They%20ache%20to%20cheer%2C%20but%20cannot%20cajole%20themselves%20into%20doing%20so.%20As%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20and%20Labuschagne%20complete%20the%20winning%20run%2C%20the%20hush%20renders%20the%20cries%20from%20the%20Australian%20dugout%20audible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20realist%20could%20well%20argue%20that%20India%20won%20this%20World%20Cup%20anyway%3A%20they%20were%20able%20to%20round%20around%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cricket%20world%20like%20traffic%20cones%20for%20six%20weeks%3B%20they%20will%20rake%20off%20almost%20four%20in%20every%20ten%20dollars%20the%20tournament%20generated.%201983%20portended%20great%20cricket%20change%3B%202023%20confirms%20little%20more%20than%20that%20Australia%20is%20represented%20by%20an%20experienced%2C%20spirited%2C%20resourceful%20cricket%20team%2C%20that%20is%20even%20now%20coming%20to%20the%20end%20of%20its%20life%20cycle.%20The%20balance%20of%20global%20cricket%20power%2C%20politically%2C%20demographically%20and%20economically%2C%20is%20fundamentally%20undisturbed%3B%20the%20BCCI%20and%20BJP%20will%20remain%20separated%20by%20a%20fag%20paper%3B%20the%20international%20game%20will%20continue%20as%20an%20elite%20racket.%20Cricket%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20had%20ten%20teams%20and%2048%20matches%3B%20football%E2%80%99s%20next%20World%20Cup%20will%20have%2048%20teams%20and%20104%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20a%20satisfaction%20elsewhere%20today%20at%20India%20finishing%20second%20%E2%80%93%20the%20same%20satisfaction%20experienced%20when%20Australia%2C%20in%20its%20pomp%2C%20was%20bested%2C%20every%20so%20often%20(2001%20in%20India%2C%202005%20in%20England%20etc).%20Nobody%20now%20would%20remember%20the%20Titanic%20had%20it%20simply%20arrived%20in%20New%20York%3B%20India%20hitting%20an%20Australian%20iceberg%20is%20an%20infinitely%20superior%20sporting%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20today%20is%20as%20much%20a%20%E2%80%98birthplace%20of%20giants%E2%80%99%20as%20England%20ever%20was.%20Gandhi%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Sardar%20Patel.%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Ravi%20Shankar%2C%20Mother%20Teresa.%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20can%20you%20hear%20me%3F%20Your%20boys%20took%20a%20hell%20of%20a%20beating!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fgideon-haigh%5C%22%3EGideon%20Haigh%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20a%20journalist%20for%20almost%20four%20decades%2C%20has%20published%20more%20than%2040%20books%20and%20contributed%20to%20more%20than%20100%20newspapers%20and%20magazines.%20He%20is%20also%20co-host%20of%20the%20podcast%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECricket%2C%20Et%20Cetera.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700464701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20124329%2FF_TytKoWgAALbGm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-australia-cricket-world-cup-final-gideon-haigh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%E2%80%99s%20where%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20timeworn%20%E2%80%98war%20minus%20the%20shooting%E2%80%99%20metaphor%20falls%20short.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-australia-cricket-world-cup-final-gideon-haigh%