on%20November%2013%2C%20saying%20that%20his%20remarks%20on%20Hindutva%20and%20it%20being%20anti-Muslim%20were%20unnecessary%20and%20objectionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Findia-israel-palestine-kashmir-azad-ressa%5C%22%3EIn%20State%20Repression%20and%20Its%20Justification%2C%20India%20and%20Israel%20Have%20Much%20in%20Common%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVanaik%20said%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20prioritise%20one%20particular%20community%2C%20this%20is%20in%20contrast%20with%20another%20conception%20of%20nationalism%2C%20which%20in%20India%20is%20that%20of%20composite%20nationalism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20many%20had%20recorded%20his%20lecture%20on%20Palestine%20and%20posted%20some%20parts%20online.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20that%20I%20am%20pro-terrorism%20is%20absolute%20nonsense.%20My%20words%20were%20absolutely%20taken%20out%20of%20context%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20want%20to%20clarify%20here%20that%20I%20do%20consider%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20action%20as%20a%20terrorist%20action%20and%20criticise%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Bombay%20had%20cancelled%20Vanaik%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20talk%20expected%20to%20throw%20light%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20and%20the%20repercussions%20of%20the%20recent%20violence%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fjindal-university-achin-vanaik-israel-palestine-lecture-9033189%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700458513000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20105752%2F7005574091_4292365d6d_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fasked-by-o-p-jindal-uni