0because%20we%20say%20so.%20Just%20as%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffive-keys-takeaways-from-the-g20-summit-in-delhi%5C%22%3Ea%20routine%20and%20rotational%20hosting%20of%20an%20international%20gathering%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20converted%20into%20an%20%E2%80%98our%20moment%20has%20come%E2%80%99%20frenzy%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98unbeaten%E2%80%99%20team%20was%20deemed%20destined%20to%20win%20just%20because%20we%20have%20%E2%80%98waited%E2%80%99%20too%20long.%20As%20part%20of%20our%20much%20proclaimed%20national%20%E2%80%98march%E2%80%99%20to%20glory%20and%20power%2C%20we%20seem%20to%20have%20concluded%20that%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20owed%20us%20a%20World%20Cup%20trophy.%20As%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPunjab%20Kesari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(that%20authentic%20voice%20of%20the%20Hindi%20heartland)%20headline%20put%20it%20on%20Sunday%20morning%3A%20%E2%80%98It%20was%20time%20to%20get%20even%20%5B%20with%20Australia%5D.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20team%20has%20every%20reason%20to%20feel%20proud%20of%20their%20campaign%2C%20winning%20the%20first%20nine%20matches%20of%20the%20tournament.%20But%20since%20the%20Cup%20has%20eluded%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20be%20skewered%20by%20the%20Monday-morning%20quarterbacks.%20In%20our%20collective%20boorishness%2C%20we%20no%20longer%20know%20how%20to%20be%20graceful%20in%20defeat.%20Cricket%20outshines%20all%20other%20sporting%20contests%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20command%20our%20attention%20and%20adulation.%20We%20are%20thus%20not%20very%20good%20particularly%20at%20taking%20a%20cricket%20defeat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20nation%20we%20were%20silently%20hoping%20for%20a%20genuine%20%E2%80%98national%20triumph%E2%80%99%20at%20Ahmedabad%2C%20a%20contest%20won%20(or%20lost)%20according%20to%20established%20rules%2C%20vigilantly%20and%20vigorously%20enforced%20by%20an%20external%20body%20and%20its%20neutral%20referees.%20Most%20of%20us%20feel%20in%20our%20bones%20that%20much%20of%20what%20we%20claim%20as%20%E2%80%98success%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98achievements%E2%80%99%20are%20carved%20out%20under%20dubious%20rules%20enforced%20by%20dubious%20and%20enfeebled%20umpires.%20Apart%20from%20a%20lustily%20cheering%20home%20crowd%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20boys%20had%20no%20undue%20advantage.%20Fair%20contests%2C%20fairly%20won%2C%20have%20a%20satisfying%20flavour%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20society%20feels%20the%20need%20for%20stars%20and%20winners%2C%20to%20bask%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20laurels%20of%20its%20sportsmen%20and%20sportswomen.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20however%2C%20we%20have%20managed%20to%20crowd%20heroes%20and%20achievers%20out%20of%20a%20national%20imagination%20that%20has%20not%20allowed%20to%20look%20beyond%20the%20%E2%80%98inspirational%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98visionary%E2%80%99%20leadership%20of%20one%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-australia-narendra-modi-stadium%5C%22%3EWatching%20Cricket%20%E2%80%93%20Now%20a%20Vehicle%20for%20the%20Political%20Elite%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20institutionalised%20personality%20cult%20does%20not%20countenance%20any%20other%20iconic%20%E2%80%98achiever.%E2%80%99%20If%20we%20look%20unsentimentally%20at%20the%20leadership%20landscape%20in%20India%2C%20other%20than%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20there%20are%20no%20recognisable%20leader%20in%20any%20area%20of%20national%20activity.%20In%20a%20country%20that%20has%20supposedly%20elevated%20the%20soldiers%20and%20their%20generals%20to%20a%20new%20and%20higher%20status%2C%20we%20do%20not%20have%20any%20officer%20commandi