el%20and%20Hamas%20are%20close%20to%20reaching%20a%20deal%20agreeing%20to%20a%20five-day%20%E2%80%9Cpause%E2%80%9D%20in%20fighting%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2023%2F11%2F18%2Fus-israel-hamas-reach-tentative-deal-pause-conflict-free-dozens-hostages%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%20This%20pause%20would%20reportedly%20be%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%20dozens%20of%20women%20and%20children%20held%20hostage%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Hamas%20are%20currently%20in%20talks%20mediated%20by%20Qatar%20in%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20detailed%2C%20six-page%20set%20of%20written%20terms%20would%20require%20all%20parties%20to%20the%20conflict%20to%20freeze%20combat%20operations%20for%20at%20least%20five%20days%20while%20an%20initial%2050%20or%20more%20hostages%20are%20released%20in%20smaller%20batches%20every%2024%20hours.%20It%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20how%20many%20of%20the%20239%20people%20believed%20to%20be%20in%20captivity%20in%20Gaza%20would%20be%20released%20under%20the%20deal.%20Overhead%20surveillance%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Ewould%20monitor%20movement%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20police%20the%20pause%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20US%20daily%20stated.%20The%20pause%20is%20also%20supposed%20to%20allow%20substantial%20humanitarian%20relief%20into%20Gaza.%20Earlier%2C%20a%20Hamas%20negotiator%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Hamas%20would%20not%20agree%20to%20overhead%20surveillance%20or%20any%20other%20movement%20in%20the%20skies%20during%20the%20pause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%20Adrienne%20Watson%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20there%20was%20no%20final%20deal%20yet%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20get%20a%20deal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20political%20bureau%20and%20presently%20head%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20international%20relations%20office%20in%20Doha%2C%20Dr%20Musa%20Abu%20Marzouq%2C%20has%20given%20extensive%20details%20of%20the%20hostage-prisoner%20exchange%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20are%20negotiating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20will%20release%2050%20Israeli%20hostages%20in%20return%20for%20Israel%20releasing%20100%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20Marzouq%20said.%C2%A0He%20said%20there%20were%20two%20conditions.%20First%2C%20Hamas%20wants%20free%20movement%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20to%20move%20both%20north-to-south%20and%20south-to-north.%20He%20said%20Israel%20has%20agreed%20to%20the%20north-south%20movement%20but%20is%20so%20far%20not%20agreeing%20to%20the%20south-north%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarzouq%20said%20the%20second%20condition%20is%20that%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20airstrikes%20completely%20stopping%20during%20the%20five-day%20ceasefire%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20movement%20in%20the%20skies%2C%20i.e.%20no%20reconnaissance%20flights%20or%20drones.%20So%20far%20Israel%20has%20not%20agreed%20to%20this%20condition%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAGL3mkKQ8ng%3Fsi%3DZ7WiAoqb7SQI8bF5%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20continues%20to%20draw%20condemnation%20from%20international%20organisations.%20United%20Nations%20Secretary%20General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20on%20Sunday%20released%20a%20statement%20condemning%20the%20strikes%20on%20two%20UNRWA%20schools%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%20are%20seeking%20shelter%20at%20United%20Nations%20facilities%20throughout%20Gaza%20due%20to%20the%20intensified%20fighting.%20I%20reaffirm%20that%20our%20premises%20are%20inviolable.%C2%A0This%20war%20is%20having%20a%20staggering%20and%20unacceptable%20number%20of%20civilian%20casualties%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20every%20day.%20This%20must%20stop%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20reiterate%20my%20call%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guterres%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20want%20to%20express%20my%20deep%20appreciation%20for%20all%20the%20mediation%20efforts%20led%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Qatar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20a%20joint%20UN%20humanitarian%20assessment%20team%20led%20by%20WHO%20accessed%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20northern%20Gaza.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20team%20was%20able%20to%20spend%20only%20one%20hour%20inside%20the%20hospital%2C%20which%20they%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20zone%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20situation%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdesperate%E2%80%9D%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20WHO%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F18-11-2023-who-leads-very-high-risk-joint-humanitarian-mission-to-al-shifa-hospital-in-gaza%5C%22%3Esaid%20later%20in%20the%20day%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLack%20of%20clean%20water%2C%20fuel%2C%20medicines%2C%20food%20and%20other%20essential%20aid%20over%20the%20last%206%20weeks%20have%20caused%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%20%E2%80%93%20once%20the%20largest%2C%20most%20advanced%20and%20best%20equipped%20referral%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20to%20essentially%20stop%20functioning%20as%20a%20medical%20facility.%20The%20team%20observed%20that%20due%20to%20the%20security%20situation%2C%20it%20has%20been%20impossible%20for%20the%20staff%20to%20carry%20out%20effective%20waste%20management%20in%20the%20hospital.%20Corridors%20and%20the%20hospital%20grounds%20were%20filled%20with%20medical%20and%20solid%20waste%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20infection.%20Patients%20and%20health%20staff%20with%20whom%20they%20spoke%20were%20terrified%20for%20their%20safety%20and%20health%2C%20and%20pleaded%20for%20evacuation.%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%20can%20no%20longer%20admit%20patients%2C%20with%20the%20injured%20and%20sick%20now%20being%20directed%20to%20the%20seriously%20overwhelmed%20and%20barely%20functioning%20Indonesian%20Hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20visit%2C%2031%20prematurely%20born%20babies%20have%20been%20evacuated%20from%20al-Shifa%20Hospital%20and%20taken%20to%20the%20European%20and%20Nasser%20hospitals%20in%20the%20south%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2023%2F11%2F19%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-israel-attacked-two-schools-killing-dozens%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Two%20babies%20died%20before%20they%20could%20be%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20troops%20have%20been%20raiding%20the%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20for%20days%20now%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F16%2Fisrael-gaza-shifa-hamas-evidence%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20not%20found%20any%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20corroborate%20its%20claims%20that%20the%20hospital%20sits%20on%20top%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20headquarters.%20The%20hospital%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20severe%20shortages%20of%20food%2C%20water%20and%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700417832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19234620%2FF_P_zHFX0AAX0nd.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-hamas-close-to-agreeing-on-five-day-pause-in-fighting-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20pause%20would%20reportedly%20be%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%20dozens%20of%20women%20and%20children%20held%20hostage%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-hamas-close-to-agreeing-on-five-day-pause-in-fight