icult%20lived%20experiences%2C%20we%20understand%20how%20it%20feels.%20For%20us%2C%20empathy%20is%20more%20important%20than%20funding%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Ya_All%20also%20opened%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20de-addiction%20centre%20for%20transgender%20men%2C%20which%20is%20run%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur.%20Called%20the%20Rainbow%20Trust%20Centre%2C%20it%20offers%20de-addiction%20and%20psychosocial%20support%20for%20two%20months%20free%20of%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20boy%20or%20girl%20identifies%20themselves%20as%20a%20transgender%20man%20or%20woman%2C%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20stay%20in%20rehabilitation%20centres%20catered%20to%20cisgender%20men%20or%20women.%20These%20aren%E2%80%99t%20safe%20spaces.%20Many%20queer%20people%20suffer%20sexual%20assault%20and%20harassment%20at%20these%20centres.%20Parents%20forcefully%20admit%20them%20into%20these%20centres%20for%20recovery%20without%20their%20consent.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20are%20working%20with%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20social%20welfare%20department%20to%20create%20this%20space%20(de-addiction%20centre)%20for%20transgender%20men.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20new%20initiative%20but%20deeply%20personal%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Safe%20spaces%20for%20Queer%20People%20in%20Manipur%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F