%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COrchids%20provide%20habitat%20and%20food%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20species%2C%20including%20pollinators%20like%20bees%20and%20butterflies.%20But%20people%20are%20hardly%20concerned%20about%20these%20plants.%20Many%20of%20its%20species%20are%20disappearing%20from%20our%20land.%20I%20wanted%20to%20conserve%20these%20plants%20so%20that%20they%20protect%20the%20environment%20and%20biodiversity.%20The%20environment%20is%20where%20all%20life%20originates%20and%20where%20everything%20we%20need%20for%20our%20survival%20comes%20from.%20We%20need%20to%20start%20respecting%20and%20protecting%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20more%20than%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20Sabu%20has%20taken%20conservation%20action%20as%20his%20hobby.%20Whenever%20he%20gets%20a%20chance%2C%20he%20sets%20out%20in%20the%20forest%20to%20collect%20and%20conserve%20wild%20orchids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20back%20to%20Mother%20Earth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20any%20experience%20in%20agricultural%20studies%2C%20Sabu%20started%20his%20own%20initiative.%20He%20follows%20the%20approach%20of%20collection%2C%20conservation%2C%20and%20augmentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20he%20collects%20wild%20orchids%20that%20grow%20on%20tree%20trunks%2C%20rocks%2C%20and%20rock%20fissures.%20After%20understanding%20the%20environment%20required%20to%20grow%20them%2C%20he%20nurtures%20and%20propagates%20them%20at%20his%20home.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20replants%20the%20plant%20species%20to%20its%20native%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20near%20the%20mother%20plant%20%E2%80%94%20without%20harming%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20this%2C%20Sabu%20observes%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20plant%20and%20documents%20it%20in%20his%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C