a%20movie.%20There%20were%20leaders%20and%20influential%20people%20all%20around%20us.%20Never%20in%20my%20dreams%20had%20I%20imagined%20that%20I%20would%20be%20in%20a%20place%20like%20that%2C%20let%20alone%20lead%20a%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20Namita%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Diwali%2C%20the%20group%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20over%203%2C000%20%3Cem%3Ekandils%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9COur%20products%20are%20sold%20all%20over%20the%20world%20including%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Australia%20and%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20remote%20villages%20to%20G20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamita%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20independence%20is%20a%20story%20infused%20with%20doses%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332290%2Fmaharashtra-water-scarcity-drought-prone-jalna-district-gets-aid-water-bodies-desilted%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einspiration%20and%20self-belief.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20her%20days%20before%20she%20learned%20the%20craft%20of%20bamboo%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20days%20would%20mostly%20revolve%20around%20cleaning%2C%20cooking%2C%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20my%20family.%20I%20would%20join%20my%20husband%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20but%20that%20was%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2029-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-4-1700058021.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Namita%20Namdev%20selling%20bamboo%20products.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-4-1700058021.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-4-170