ia%20and%20Sports%20and%20Society%20Accelerator.%20The%20series%20celebrates%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20with%20stories%20of%20heroes%20who%20have%20spent%20years%20working%20to%20improve%20lives%20around%20them%20through%20sports.%20Stay%20tuned%20for%20inspiring%20tales%20of%20those%20who%20are%20%23MakingSportWork.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20graduation%2C%20Bengaluru-based%20Vishal%20Talreja%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20visit%20Finland%2C%20where%20he%20noticed%20a%20significant%20emphasis%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20dignity%20of%20labour%20and%20the%20high%20quality%20of%20life%20that%20people%20enjoyed%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20background%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20got%20me%20thinking%20about%20my%20own%20upbringing%20and%20the%20caste-class%20system%20surrounding%20us.%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20back%20to%20India%20and%20change%20the%20way%20we%20look%20at%20dignity%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20returning%20to%20his%20homeland%2C%20Vishal%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20his%20weekends%20to%20meaningful%20volunteer%20work.%20He%20focused%20on%20assisting%20youth%20from%20underprivileged%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F239494%2Fonline-education-classes-how-to-volunteer-covid19-distance-teaching-ngos-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evulnerable%20backgrounds%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20they%20were%20exposed%20to%20issues%20such%20as%20malnutrition%2C%20abuse%2C%20and%20exposure%20to%20crime%20at%20an%20early%20age.%20Education%20and%20life%20skills%20were%20not%20prioritised%20for%20this%20group%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20offer%20his%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20various%20connections%2C%20he%20met%20a%20group%20of%20passionate%20people%2C%20all%20in%20their%20early%2020s%20working%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Delhi.%20Although%20they%2