n%20the%20garment%20industry.%20Because%20of%20financial%20constraints%2C%20we%20did%20not%20get%20good%20quality%20food%20at%20home.%20I%20mostly%20depended%20on%20the%20snacks%20provided%20by%20Dream%20a%20Dream%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-3-1700039287.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dream%20a%20dream%20directly%20engages%20with%2010%2C000%20children%20each%20year%2C%20offering%20innovative%20education%20opportunities%20through%20sports%20and%20arts.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-3-1700039287.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-3-1700039287-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-3-1700039287-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-3-1700039287-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-3-1700039287-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334166%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDream%20a%20Dream%20directly%20engages%20with%2010%2C000%20children%20each%20year%2C%20offering%20innovative%20education%20opportunities%20through%20sports%20and%20arts.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20support%20himself%20financially%2C%20he%20took%20on%20part-time%20jobs%2C%20including%20assisting%20in%20garment%20work%20and%20distributing%20newspapers.%20Despite%20the%20challenges%20he%20encountered%20at%20home%2C%20within%20a%20few%20years%2C%20Ranjith%20was%20competing%20at%20the%20national%20level%20for%20Karnata