other)%20would%20put%20the%20last%20finishing%20touches%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333532%2Fpadma-shri-t-s-satyan-father-of-indian-photojournalism-mysuru-bengaluru-history-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintricate%20paintings%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20home%E2%80%99s%20mud%20walls%2C%20a%20young%20Durgabai%20watched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArt%2C%20therefore%2C%20was%20her%20first%20subject%2C%20a%20love%20she%20carried%20with%20her%20through%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20Dindori%2C%20I%20would%20paint%20on%20the%20walls%20using%20white%20mud%20(%3Cem%3Echuhi%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20red%20mud%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20black%20mud%20(charcoal%20black).%20Festivals%20and%20weddings%20in%20the%20village%20were%20my%20favourite%20occasions%20since%20there%20would%20be%20opportunities%20for%20me%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Edignas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20form%20of%20tribal%20art%20practised%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Gond%20community)%20on%20the%20home%20walls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20at%2050%2C%20one%20would%20say%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333114%2Fkolkata-artist-kishore-pratim-biswas-paints-steam-locomotives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eart%20is%20in%20her%20genes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20she%20replicates%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20style.%20This%20time%20on%20canvas%20and%20walls%20that%20are%20hundreds%20of%20feet%20tall.%20Vyam%E2%80%99s%20artistic%20prowess%20led%20her%20to%20win%20many%20accolades%20throughout%20her%20career%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prestigious%20being%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20her%20niche%20in%20the%20art%20world%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20from%20mud%20walls%20to%20canvas%20happened%20in%201996%20when%20Durgabai%20married%20S